OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry, hazy day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine and widely hot
OL,7,Ftemperatures. Light winds will offer
OL,8,Flittle relief though a gentle sea
OL,9,Fbreeze may develop close to the coast
OL,10,Ftaking the edge off the temperature.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry, mostly clear but humid
OL,13,Fnight is expected with light winds.
OL,14,FSome patchy mist may form inland and
OL,15,Falong the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry with long sunny periods
OL,18,Fand light winds. Widely very warm or
OL,19,Fhot with heatwave conditions expected,
OL,20,Fincluding overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
